 Test Annotations
 --------------
 test.only -->focus the tests marked only
 test.skip -->skipped from the execution
 test.fixme --> marks the test needs fix
 test.fail -->make the test fail  -->pass -status
 test.slow -->triple the default timout 
 test.describe -->to group -->  default,serial, parallel , retries
 test.info -->provides the information on current running test ->title, status

 -------------
 test.beforeAll -->reporter -->execute only once among all the test
 test.beforeEach -->before for each test 
 test.afterEach  -->after each test 
 test.afterAll --after all the test
----------
  
 
  
Assessment: 
1 Launch the browser and navigate to https://www.tatacliq.com/. 
2  Mouse hover on the “Brands” menu option. 
3  Mouse hover on “Watches & Accessories” under the Brands submenu. 
4  From the “Featured Brands”, click the first brand option that appears. 
5  On the brand listing page, select "Sort By: New Arrivals" from the sort dropdown. 
6  Under the left sidebar filters, expand “Categories” and select “Men”. 
7  Wait for product list to update and print all the prices of displayed watches. 
8  Click on the first watch from the resulting product grid. 
9  If any alert popup appears (e.g. confirmation or promo), handle it accordingly. 
10  On the watch detail page, compare the price shown here with the one from the listing page. 
11 Click the "Add to Cart" button. 
12 Capture the item count from the cart icon. 
13 Click the cart icon to view the cart. 
14 Take a screenshot of the cart page. 
15 Close all the opened windows/tabs one by one. 
  
Assessment :2 
1) Launch the app login.salesforce.com 
2) Login with the credentials (Use json file to read the credentials)
3) Click Login
4) Click App Launcher
5) Click ViewAll
6) Search Contacts
7) click Contacts
8) Click New Contact
9) Pick Salutation as 'Mr.'
10) Enter First Name
11) Enter Last Name 
12) Enter email 
Note: use csv file to read first name , lastname and email
13) Create a New Account for Account Name
14) Enter account name as 'Credits' and save
15) Click and save
16) Verify contact using Unique name and print the name













